You will need:
 - Current directory defined in ALIGNKALDI_ROOT environment variable
 - Kaldi tree compiled and KALDI_ROOT environment variable
 - Textnorm scripts and TEXTNORM_ROOT environment variable
 - OpenFST installed (on the PATH)
 - SoX installed (on the PATH)
 - PyOpenFST installed (on the PYTHONPATH)
 - Sequitur installed and on the PYTHONPATH

